        <div>
            <h2>Danh sách booking</h2>
            <p>Tập trung lifecycle: Pending → Confirmed → CheckedIn → CheckedOut.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="badge-soft badge-confirmed">85 booking</span>
    </div>

    <div class="table-wrap">
